{"items":[{"id":"47054","user":{"id":"118178","nickname":"主播喵","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FvoBGcSVvSx_sjM_nrtVqTkv94de","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p><img src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/d8/good_thumb.gif\"><br></p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1507517306,"created_at":1507517306,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"46142","user":{"id":"315401","nickname":"谌轩","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FuCAN8yKqmmhqCJDwzx3a27wFRYY?attname=","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>人们，永远不知道宇宙之外是什么。</p>\n<p>至于所谓科学家的见解只是因为科技的不发达而封闭我们脑洞的”理论“。</p>\n<p>因为我们主观认为宇宙便是我们生存的空间。</p>\n<p>但是有没有想过这样一种假设。宇宙是”外面人“的水晶玩具呢？</p>\n<p>我们有许多假设，但却被各种”理论’埋没了。</p>\n<p>说不定呢、</p>\n<p>也是因为我们对这个宇宙，这个奇迹般的东西了解太少。</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 摘自《知乎》</p>\n<p>不喜勿喷</p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1507261483,"created_at":1507261483,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"46103","user":{"id":"333030","nickname":"罗兴懿","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FoVor7_eU0nOluhuVu0qTU_PD7wL","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p><p>@前·方·高·能·之·辣·稽 支持</p></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1507218772,"created_at":1507218772,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"46076","user":{"id":"179794","nickname":"ftxqgfudi","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/community_frontend/community_default_avatar/avatar_300x300_01.jpg","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>额……根本没可能回到过去……所以这两种假想都不成立好吧……</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1507206899,"created_at":1507206899,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"46075","user":{"id":"183448","nickname":"喆","avatar_url":"https://static-platform.codemao.cn/production/avatar/custom/971d51d0-a814-42c6-b9c2-771573cc536f","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>图3的时间线与图4没有关联所以我支持2. 平行宇宙</p>\n<p>历史的不同选择会产生不同的结局，并形成不同的平行宇宙。</p>\n<br>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1507206671,"created_at":1507206671,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"46074","user":{"id":"183448","nickname":"喆","avatar_url":"https://static-platform.codemao.cn/production/avatar/custom/971d51d0-a814-42c6-b9c2-771573cc536f","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>我支持2. 平行宇宙</p>\n<p>历史的不同选择会产生不同的结局，并形成不同的平行宇宙。</p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1507206407,"created_at":1507206407,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"46040","user":{"id":"206348","nickname":"Monica老莫","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fjln215RiKU5IjvGRd-KqQiJh8AL?attname=","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>我支持平行宇宙理论，我坚信这个宇宙的外面还是一个宇宙。那个宇宙里面有一个Monica老莫，有一个编程猫，有这里一切的东西，只是现在在电脑前打字的Monica和另一个Monica做着不一样的事情。</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1507199666,"created_at":1507199666,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"46023","user":{"id":"138888","nickname":"碳烤小火龙","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/9954dbdc-d73a-45d9-9571-869a662b55fd","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p><p>支持平行宇宙概念 +1</p></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1507197295,"created_at":1507197295,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"46022","user":{"id":"315401","nickname":"谌轩","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FuCAN8yKqmmhqCJDwzx3a27wFRYY?attname=","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>我支持平行宇宙概念</p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1507196362,"created_at":1507196362,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"45565","user":{"id":"179794","nickname":"ftxqgfudi","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/community_frontend/community_default_avatar/avatar_300x300_01.jpg","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>有一种人，他们从一出生便能知道一生的事情，知道以后会发生什么，但是却无法记住发生了什么，所以，他们出生时洞察一世，死前却一无所知。</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1506997300,"created_at":1506997300,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"45564","user":{"id":"179233","nickname":"杰鸽","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fj9WL32g3J_9Om1sWroOWquXZ25U","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>如果成功拆散，那么就不可能有你；</p>\n<p>如果没有，那这就是喵，等同于上帝存在，让你绝对无法做到某事</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1506996532,"created_at":1506996532,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"45558","user":{"id":"217715","nickname":"乐乐在此","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FuROoLwEt0lSCjhsUc7wklTuB28j","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p><img src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/cc/haqianv2_thumb.gif\">&nbsp;<br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1506994076,"created_at":1506994076,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"45267","user":{"id":"179233","nickname":"杰鸽","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fj9WL32g3J_9Om1sWroOWquXZ25U","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>喵啊</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1506819266,"created_at":1506819266,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"45266","user":{"id":"179233","nickname":"杰鸽","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fj9WL32g3J_9Om1sWroOWquXZ25U","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p><i>过去和未来都发生在一个宇宙中，但时间旅行者不管怎么做无法影响过去。</i>不仅无法影响过去，时间旅行还是历史的一部分，一切都是必然。在这种设定下，因果是循环的。隐含观点就是过去现在未来都是定死的。</p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1506819252,"created_at":1506819252,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"45231","user":{"id":"102324","nickname":"你昨晚上是真的不行","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FgM4kQ7IP_XdBQCXygzJeX-oyJZo","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>最好的解释就是</p>\n<p>为什么没有来自未来的旅游者呢？</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1506778833,"created_at":1506778833,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"45144","user":{"id":"348908","nickname":"廿一","avatar_url":"https://static-user-center.codemao.cn/user_0009.png","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>这个【外祖父悖论】啊，可能是成立的，可能是不成立的，从量子力学的角度来说，这个成立和不成立它是平行存在前进的，只有真正回到过去阻止外祖父与外祖母感情进展那瞬间，这两种可能性，才坍缩到一种可能性上，要么是成立坍缩到不成立，要么是不成立坍缩到成立，这就是一个非常著名的定理，叫薛定谔的猫。<br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1506690484,"created_at":1506690484,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"45045","user":{"id":"314171","nickname":"假编程猫258","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/47/community/d2ViXzEwMDFfMzE0MTcxXzMxNDE3MV8xNjU4Mzg4OTczNzc3XzMzMDRiYTk5.png","subject_id":211,"work_shop_name":"跃动工作室","work_shop_level":3,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>我支持平行宇宙</p>\n<p>关于蝴蝶效应</p>\n<p>假设一个人天丢一个塑料袋，一年后他居住的那个国家会全是塑料袋</p>\n<p>其实穿梭时空有争议</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1506603705,"created_at":1506603705,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"44995","user":{"id":"179233","nickname":"杰鸽","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fj9WL32g3J_9Om1sWroOWquXZ25U","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>@二楼</p>\n<p>你怎么确定天下本来的样子不是乱的呢？</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1506592638,"created_at":1506592638,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"44982","user":{"id":"332080","nickname":"阿鹅","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FtYsJPXG1kygEDpsS8RRSLSy2Qcm","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>@<a rel=\"nofollow\">前方高能之辣稽</a></p>\n<p>哈哈哈这个只是个假设而已啦</p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1506576889,"created_at":1506576889,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"44981","user":{"id":"332080","nickname":"阿鹅","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FtYsJPXG1kygEDpsS8RRSLSy2Qcm","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>@<a rel=\"nofollow\">|糖醋排骨|</a></p>\n<p>穿越有风险，行事需谨慎</p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1506576864,"created_at":1506576864,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"44954","user":{"id":"134663","nickname":"时间拓荒者","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Ft3HPncaTFz31t5GLl5ej20heFkT","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>我同意平行宇宙</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1506521910,"created_at":1506521910,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"44953","user":{"id":"198778","nickname":"糖醋排骨","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/47/community/d2ViXzEwMDFfMTk4Nzc4XzE5ODc3OF8xNjEzOTE2MzY2ODg0Xzg3NDhjODY5.png","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>其实自己的外祖父或外祖母的选择就决定了我们。比如外祖父要面临三个妻子的选择：外祖母、喵路人甲与喵路人乙。如果我们穿越回去跟外祖父说一些垃圾谬论，可能导致选择的不是外祖母，那么自己就不可能存在……不要穿越啊喵年</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1506521469,"created_at":1506521469,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"44940","user":{"id":"179794","nickname":"ftxqgfudi","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/community_frontend/community_default_avatar/avatar_300x300_01.jpg","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>这个果会导致因不成立，从而果不成立，那么因就会成立的事情就是悖论。</p>\n<p>对此，霍金认为：就不可能回到过去！</p>\n<p>我们可以超前到未来，但是不能够回到过去，这个根本条件就不成立。</p>\n<p>霍金把这个叫做“反馈”。</p>\n<p>反馈是啥？</p>\n<p>一个话筒，一个音箱。</p>\n<p>话筒说话从音箱放出来，然后被话筒采集，不断循环……</p>\n<p>这就是反馈。</p>\n<p>回到过去的反馈现象是不成立的，而一个造成了不成立反馈的事情本身就是不成立的。</p>\n<p>说也解释不明白，我有纪录片，一会儿发链接，自己看看。</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1506513970,"created_at":1506513970,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"44918","user":{"id":"204645","nickname":"小假LittleFalse","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fqw3NfVBhmglR3dOjGtkKh5J2oXD","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>我同意维科夫自洽性原则</p>\n<p>假设阿短回去过去，拆散了阿短的外祖母和外祖父，假设成功</p>\n<p>则阿短不会出现，若是阿短不会出现，那么阿短的外祖母和外祖父就不会被拆散，那么阿短还会出现，两个条件互相矛盾</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1506505318,"created_at":1506505318,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"44916","user":{"id":"139365","nickname":"韵律源点Arcaea","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/47/community/d2ViXzEwMDFfMTM5MzY1XzEzOTM2NV8xNjU0MDAxNjQ0NTE5XzI3MGQwOTRh.png","subject_id":5482,"work_shop_name":"咕咕咕咕咕咕咕（）","work_shop_level":2,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>我支持诺维科夫自洽性原则！</p>\n<p>如果能改变历史，那不就世界大乱了吗！</p>\n<p>所以我支持诺维科夫自洽性原则！<br></p>\n<p>还有！</p>\n<p>如果我回到历史，我也不会像上面的阿短一样！</p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1506504246,"created_at":1506504246,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"44915","user":{"id":"194938","nickname":"提米","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/47/community/d2ViXzEwMDFfMTk0OTM4XzE5NDkzOF8xNjAzNTMwOTg5OTg0XzlkOTRkY2U3.png","subject_id":214,"work_shop_name":"疯癫工作室","work_shop_level":3,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>沙发！<img src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/4a/mm_thumb.gif\"></p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1506503627,"created_at":1506503627,"earliest_comments":[]}],"offset":0,"limit":30,"total":26,"counted":true}